text: Zokhid Kenjaev (born March 30, 1992) is an Uzbekistani table tennis player. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's singles event, in which he was eliminated in the second round by Liam Pitchford. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani male table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Uzbekistan Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics
